    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a fantastic car. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-cared for over the years. It\u2019s perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend road trips! It runs beautifully and is just waiting for someone new to take it on some adventures. Come check it out and see for yourself\u2014I'd love for it to go to a great home!",
      "price": 32500.0,
